紀元, 但確有其事"},{"pid":"a36d6d59f65d2ec3215613bfdfabb84a1c450382","tid":1655371,"uid":220853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"所有隕石必須經過國家安全管理審核 和認證<br />\n唯有取得政府批准許可 隕石才可以墜落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a9c3d5af1113122892f25b4d1001e999d8174e","tid":1655371,"uid":61976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"毛說，要死人<br />\n就死了人"},{"pid":"cdb6d8d0256a1237064a682d3a97882ca9000e6e","tid":1655371,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"毛=豬頭<br />\n周=李克強<br />\n朱=粟戰書/王歧山"}]}